**Veteran** | Townsfolk Killing
__Basics__
The **veteran** may choose to alert at night. They will kill any player who visits them whilst alert.

__Formalized__
Passive Start Day: Set Counter to 0
Fourth Pre-End Night: Set Counter to 1 [Quantity: %Number%] |veteran.1|
On Visited: Process: Attack @Visitor [Condition: @Self->Counter is 1]
